This paper deals with the construction of commonsense knowledge graphs using natural language texts, which involves tasks such as relation extraction, entity linking, and triple classification. These tasks are closely related to several sub-fields of computer science, including natural language processing (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), information retrieval (cs.IR), and social and information networks (cs.SI). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
